description:
## Foundation Design System

### Color Palette (finalized)
```css
:root {
  /* Primary */
  --color-accent: #FF6B35;        /* Orange - CTAs, highlights */
  --color-accent-hover: #E55A2B;  /* Darker orange */

  /* Neutrals */
  --color-bg: #F5F0E8;            /* Sand/cream - page background */
  --color-bg-alt: #EDE5D8;        /* Slightly darker sand */
  --color-dark: #2D2D2D;          /* Charcoal - text */
  --color-dark-soft: #4A4A4A;     /* Softer charcoal */

  /* Desert accents */
  --color-warm: #D4A574;          /* Sandstone */
  --color-sky: #87CEEB;           /* Outback sky blue */
  --color-earth: #8B4513;         /* Red earth */

  /* Shadows */
  --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --shadow-md: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  --shadow-lg: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}
```

### Typography
**Fonts:**
- Headings: Inter or similar sans-serif (system-ui fallback)
- Body: Inter
- Code: JetBrains Mono or Fira Code

**Scale (fluid):**
```css
--text-xs: clamp(0.75rem, 0.7rem + 0.25vw, 0.875rem);
--text-sm: clamp(0.875rem, 0.8rem + 0.35vw, 1rem);
--text-base: clamp(1rem, 0.9rem + 0.5vw, 1.125rem);
--text-lg: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 1vw, 1.5rem);
--text-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1.5vw, 2rem);
--text-2xl: clamp(2rem, 1.5rem + 2.5vw, 3rem);
--text-hero: clamp(3rem, 2rem + 5vw, 6rem);
```

### Spacing System
```css
--space-1: 0.25rem;  /* 4px */
--space-2: 0.5rem;   /* 8px */
--space-3: 0.75rem;  /* 12px */
--space-4: 1rem;     /* 16px */
--space-6: 1.5rem;   /* 24px */
--space-8: 2rem;     /* 32px */
--space-12: 3rem;    /* 48px */
--space-16: 4rem;    /* 64px */
--space-24: 6rem;    /* 96px */
```

### Animation Tokens (from research)
```css
--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
--ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
--ease-bounce: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
--duration-fast: 0.15s;
--duration-normal: 0.3s;
--duration-slow: 0.6s;
--stagger: 0.1s;
```

